            "size": 1073,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01MXCLctKHU98V1it9J6WLYC\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01EjD4r4hTwHsKxWZET8uQif\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"success\":false,\"reasoning\":\"The answer \\\"Pasta is so good it makes me want to die\\\" is not a business idea at all. It's a personal opinion about food with no actionable business information. It fails on all four criteria: (1) Not specific to any business model, (2) Not actionable—can't write marketing copy from this, (3) Not authentic business reasoning, and (4) Shows no understanding of a business problem or audience. The user hasn't answered the question about what they do, who it's for, what makes it different, or why it matters. This needs a complete restart with an actual business concept.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1091,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":177,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
