            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 2040,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_012V1K1ygJMksyD2a2axTovn\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01T8ba7e1yeVEnxpnZn87uie\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"success\":true,\"reasoning\":\"This answer meets all four criteria and passes the landing page test:\\n\\n**Specific** ✓ - Not vague. Clearly targets podcast hosts looking for guests. Mentions 100+ filters, AI matching on specific criteria (content, audience, goals), and a proprietary model trained on successful pitch data.\\n\\n**Actionable** ✓ - You can absolutely write landing page copy from this. Clear sections emerge: \\\"How it works\\\" (AI matching on 3 dimensions), \\\"Why choose us\\\" (trained on successful pitches from top shows), \\\"What you get\\\" (filtered guest recommendations).\\n\\n**Authentic** ✓ - Uses their actual language and process. No marketing jargon. \\\"Trained proprietary models on messages that successful podcast hosts receive\\\" is specific and real, not buzzwords.\\n\\n**Insightful** ✓ - Shows they understand the problem (hosts get bad pitches) and their solution (filter based on what actually works). The differentiator—training on successful pitch data—demonstrates understanding of the actual pain point.\\n\\n**Bonus elements present:**\\n- Unique mechanism: Proprietary models trained on successful pitches (strong differentiator)\\n- Clear outcome: Better guest matches, filtered out bad fits\\n- Specific process: AI matching on content/audience/goals + predictive filtering\\n- Credibility signal: \\\"100+ filters\\\" and \\\"trained on successful hosts\\\"\\n\\nThe only minor weakness is slight repetition (\\\"We use AI to match...\\\" appears twice), but this doesn't undermine the quality. You could write compelling copy immediately from this.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1643,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":393,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
