          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"success\":{\"type\":\"boolean\",\"description\":\"Was the question answered successfully? Does it include enough context to write great marketing copy for the business?\"},\"reasoning\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"Explain using the criteria why the question was or was not answered successfully.\"}},\"required\":[\"success\",\"reasoning\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n        # QA Evaluation Criteria\\n\\nALL answers must meet ALL four:\\n\\n1. **Specific** - Not vague (could describe 1000 businesses = fail)\\n2. **Actionable** - Can write marketing copy directly from it\\n3. **Authentic** - Their words, not marketing jargon (\\\"leverage synergies\\\" = fail)\\n4. **Insightful** - Shows understanding of business/audience\\n\\nClose but missing one element = NOT GREAT yet. Be critical but fair.\\n\\nOutput JSON: `{ success: boolean, reasoning: string }`\\n\\n        \\n        # QA: Social Proof\\n\\n**Social proof is broader than testimonials**: founder story, background, personal results, research, community size all count.\\n\\n**For early-stage (no testimonials)**: Founder credibility, personal transformation, process credibility, relatability = valid proof\\n\\n**High-impact proof** (Hormozi):\\n- Quantified results: \\\"Average client adds $50K\\\"\\n- Specific case studies with numbers\\n- Volume: \\\"500+ businesses\\\"\\n- Authority: \\\"Featured in Forbes\\\"\\n\\n**Reject**:\\n- \\\"I don't have testimonials\\\" without offering alternatives\\n- Generic praise without specifics (\\\"clients love me\\\")\\n- Vague credentials (\\\"10 years experience\\\" without context)\\n\\n**Privacy/NDA** → industry descriptors OK (\\\"Fortune 500 SaaS\\\")\\n\\n        \\n        <current_topic>socialProof</current_topic>\\n        \\n        <user_answer>Over 10k creators use Friend of the Pod to find guests for their shows. They are all notable names like LeBron James, Serena Williams, and Oprah Winfrey.</user_answer>\\n        \\n        <existing_memory>No answer yet</existing_memory>\\n        \\n        <task>\\n        Evaluate if their answer is GREAT based on the criteria above.\\n        Output JSON: { \\\"success\\\": boolean, \\\"reasoning\\\": string }\\n        </task>\\n    \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1668,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1668,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01Y4gBfyDj6JrGaqMGb8hi6r\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_0163dHCRdpivV7aCYziZXLcm\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"success\":false,\"reasoning\":\"The answer fails on **Authenticity** and **Specificity**. \\n\\n**Problems:**\\n1. **Not Authentic** - Claiming LeBron James, Serena Williams, and Oprah Winfrey are \\\"users\\\" of Friend of the Pod is almost certainly false. These are A-list celebrities who wouldn't need a platform to find podcast guests. This reads as fabricated social proof, which is a major red flag.\\n\\n2. **Lacks Specificity** - \\\"Over 10k creators\\\" is vague without context. Which creators? What's their reach? What results did they get? This could describe many platforms.\\n\\n3. **Missing Actionable Details** - There's no concrete outcome. Did users grow their audience? Get better guests? Increase revenue? Without results, this doesn't help write marketing copy.\\n\\n4. **Weak on Insight** - The answer doesn't demonstrate understanding of the actual value proposition or the real audience's pain point.\\n\\n**What would work instead:** Real case studies with actual creators (names optional if under NDA), quantified results (\\\"Creators averaged 40% more downloads after using Friend of the Pod\\\"), or specific industry descriptors (\\\"Used by 10k+ indie podcasters in tech and business niches\\\").\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1182,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":323,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
