            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01DAQgRDAHpGL114bF15rZca\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01GP7hH9R2JZDDjGhi1iARxc\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"success\":false,\"reasoning\":\"No answer has been provided yet. The user has asked \\\"What is your business?\\\" but there is no response to evaluate. To assess whether an answer meets the criteria (Specific, Actionable, Authentic, Insightful), I need the actual business description. Currently, there is nothing to evaluate against the QA criteria.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1535,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":117,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
